<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contributing</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f5; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;">
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%; background-color: #f4f4f5;">
    <tr>
        <td style="padding: 20px;">
            <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <div style="text-align: center; padding: 30px 20px; background: linear-gradient(to top right, #d81f3d, #fe4a2b);">
                            <img src="<%= links.mail["gamma-logo"]%>" style=" width: 90px; aspect-ratio: 1/1; border: 3px solid white; border-radius: 50%; padding:10px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: #d71e3d;" />
                            <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 24px;">CHARUSAT Hacktoberfest 2024</h1>
                            <p style="color: #ffffff; margin-top: 15px; font-size: 18px;">Contribute, Learn & Win! üèÜ</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="padding: 30px;">
                            <h2 style="color: #111827; font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 15px;">Dear Contributor,</h2>
                            <p style="color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;">Thank you for your valuable contributions to Club Gamma! Your efforts help us build a stronger community and foster collaboration among our members.</p>

                            <p style="color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;">We appreciate your commitment and look forward to your continued involvement. Together, we can achieve great things!</p>

                            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                                <a href="<%= links.website %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #d71e3d; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">Visit Club Gamma</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!--   footer    -->

                        <div style="background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
                            <p style="color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 20px;">Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:gce@charusat.edu.in" style="color: #d71e3d; text-decoration: none;">gce@charusat.edu.in</a></p>

                            <!-- Social Links -->
                            <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
                                <a href="<%= links.socials.github%>" style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;"><img src="<%= links.mail.github%>" alt="GitHub" style="width: 30px;"></a>
                                <a href="<%= links.socials.instagram%>" style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;"><img src="<%= links.mail.instagram%>" alt="Instagram" style="width: 30px;"></a>
                                <a href="<%= links.socials.twitter%>" style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;"><img src="<%= links.mail.twitter%>" alt="Twitter" style="width: 30px;"></a>
                                <a href="<%= links.socials.linkedin%>" style="display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;"><img src="<%= links.mail.linkedin%>" alt="LinkedIn" style="width: 30px;"></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
